Games-Bettor

This module and the associated modules under Bettor/* represent bettors using different types of betting
systems.  Each can be passed various pieces of information that help them decide what their wager on each
trial should be.  

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command.

    perldoc Games::Bettor

You can also look for information at:

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Games-Bettor

    CPAN Request Tracker:
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Games-Bettor

    AnnoCPAN, annotated CPAN documentation:
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Games-Bettor

    CPAN Ratings:
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Games-Bettor

